3.4.0.name: drupal/fb_registration

security-coverage.message: Covered by Drupal's security advisory policy

3.4.0.description: (fb_registration.module) Replaces Drupal user registration form with facebook registration. Note: this module is for a specific feature which facebook calls "registration", not to be confused with Drupal's user registration. Don't enable this module unless you know exactly why you need it! (fb_user.module is probably what you want.)
